On Windows you need to download wget utility. You can download it from here:
http://gnuwin32.sourceforge.net/packages/wget.htm

Or just grab this direct link:
http://downloads.sourceforge.net/gnuwin32/wget-1.11.4-1-setup.exe

Copy installed files to this directory. They are those:

libeay32.dll
libiconv2.dll
libintl3.dll
libssl32.dll
wget.exe